174. Telegram From the Department of State to the Embassy in AlgeriaSource: Department of State, Central
                        Foreign Policy File, Electronic Telegrams, [no N number]. Secret; Flash;
                        Nodis. Drafted by Stephen Grummon (S/CT);
                        cleared by Ussery, Joseph Lake
                            (S/S), Gregory Delawie (S/S–O), and Bremer; approved by Armacost. Sent for information Immediate
                        to Nicosia and Kuwait City.
